a\n- Streamlined client cash data management by implementing an automated data ingestion framework for uploading and downloading client data; projected to save 300 work hours annually"},{"key":"pacificcapital-201905","name":"Pacific Capital","date":"May 2019 - Aug. 2019","image":"static/media/pacificcapital.32d8ab91.png","icon":"static/media/pacificcapital.icon.5d81ad4d.png","website":"https://www.pacificcapital.com","position":"Quantitative Analytics Intern","team":"Portfolio Management","location":"Newport Beach, CA","detail":"- Designed reusable investment operations modules in Python that standardized Bloomberg feed parsing, computed market metrics, and automated recurring operations reporting\n- Architected and deployed an Oracle SQL database with ETL pipelines to consolidate financial data for 120+ clients from raw sources, automating data retrieval and eliminating manual data entry\n- Modeled tail-risk exposure using a volatility-weighted Python risk tool and regression analysis on historical market data under 10% S&P 500 decline scenarios"}],"hobbies":[{"key":"ski-200101","name":"Ski","image":"static/media/ski.0156853d.png","detail":"Hitting the slopes most winters — mostly groomers, occasionally chasing powder days.\n\n**Regular Resorts:**  \nBig Bear Mountain Resort  \nMammoth Mountain  \nKeystone Resort  \nNiseko United"},{"key":"badminton-200012","name":"Badminton","image":"static/media/badminton.61431557.png","detail":"Regular doubles player — always up for a fast rally."},{"key":"weight_training-200011","name":"Weight Training","image":"static/media/weight_training.17323d0b.png","detail":"Chasing progressive overload — see \"Protein for a Week\" in the PayPal menu."},{"key":"kendo-200010","name":"Kendo","image":"static/media/kendo.0dcfcec5.png","detail":"Nidan (二段, 2nd dan) in Japanese swordsmanship.\n\n**Highlights:**  \n2nd place, AUSKF state tournament (high school)\n\n**Previous Affiliations:**  \n[All United States Kendo Federation (AUSKF)](https: