e":"http://www.skycpa.com/","position":"Accounting Intern","location":"Diamond Bar, CA","detail":"- Managed and executed bank reconciliations and detailed general ledger analysis for 70+ client accounts using QuickBooks, identifying discrepancies and ensuring 100% consistency between bank statements and internal records\n- Prepared and finalized balance sheets and income statements for over 80 small business clients, providing key financial insights that were essential for clients' strategic decision-making and accurate assessment of their financial health\n- Designed and implemented a systematic tracking spreadsheet that accurately categorized and measured employee utilization rates, directly supporting and informing the company's major re-organization at the close of the 2017 fiscal year"},{"key":"masterkey-201405","name":"Master Key Education","date":"May 2014 - Aug. 2021","image":"static/media/masterkey.e02c60ef.png","position":"Math Instructor","location":"Irvine, CA","detail":"- Launched a private tutoring and college counseling organization, guiding 40+ college applicants to admission into top 50 universities by providing comprehensive support in academic strategy, extracurricular growth, and application readiness\n- Analyzed California's Annual Common Core math standards to construct updated advanced curriculums; increased 73% of students' SAT math scores to 780+ (98th percentile) and 87% of students' AMC 10/11 scores to the 90th percentile\n- Recruited and mentored a team of high-achieving tutors, developing standardized training protocols and quality control measures to ensure consistent, high-impact instruction across all client engagements"}]};